      "rdf:value": "<L>100888<pc>514,3<k1>DARaka<k2>DARaka<e>1\r\n<s>DARaka</s> ¦ <lex>m.</lex> (√ <hom>1.</hom> <s>DA</s>? <ab>cf.</ab> <ls>Uṇ. iii, 83</ls>) a weight of gold, part of a <s1>Dīnāra</s1> (<ab>cf.</ab> <hom>2.</hom> <s>DAn˚</s>), <ls>L.</ls><info lex=\"m\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
